Interface Group

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Activity, com.faizsiegeln.njams.messageformat.v4.logmessage.interfaces.IActivity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SubProcessActivity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GroupImpl, SubProcessActivityImpl

    public interface Group
extends Activity
    Activity which represents a group in a process. A group can have child activities.
    Author:
    pnientiedt
